 
<p>
Amnesty International criticized Ukraine for stationing military units
and 
<a href="https://www.amnesty.org/en/latest/news/2022/08/ukraine-ukrainian-fighting-tactics-endanger-civilians/"> weapons systems in cities.</a>
<p>
It would be absurd to compare this with the pervasive evil of the
Putin forces, and it certainly doesn't excuse them.  But this is a
valid point.  Ukraine should heed this criticism and change those
practices.

 